rule-16-5-a.test_description: A building with an elevator has the baseline elevator cab ventilation fan and lights running continuously, as expected.

standard.rule_description: When included in the proposed design, the baseline elevator cab ventilation fan and lights shall operate continuously

rule-16-5-b.test_description: A building with an elevator has baseline elevator cab ventilation fan and lighting which do not run continuously.

standard.rule_description: When included in the proposed design, the baseline elevator cab ventilation fan and lights shall operate continuously

rule-16-5-c.test_description: A proposed building design has an elevator. The baseline does not have an elevator. The failing outcome is bypassed here because it is captured in another rule.

standard.rule_description: When included in the proposed design, the baseline elevator cab ventilation fan and lights shall operate continuously

rule-16-5-d.test_description: A baseline building design has an elevator. The proposed does not have an elevator. The failing outcome is bypassed here because it is captured in another rule.

standard.rule_description: When included in the proposed design, the baseline elevator cab ventilation fan and lights shall operate continuously
